    @Named(value="com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.DefaultClassDataForClassificationService")
public class DefaultClassDataForClassificationService
extends Object
implements ClassDataForClassificationService

    This service enables you to create, read, update and delete class data, that is valid on a given date.
